                   @{"              Register              " link REGO}

 The Door works perfectly, and no limitations. Selecting [S] from the menu
 displays the system info. This system is currently GREMLiNS BBS, and is
 the text extract from the BBS Listings. If ya want to have your system
 shown, then let me know via mail, or call my BBS and request it, and I'll
 send ya your copy of the Door, with your BBS System details. CooL?!

 The reason for this is to have some response to the Door ...

@endnode
